version_description: Easier to play in the capo 2 position for the early beginner. Chord assignments are accurate for phrasing.
It's a NEW version of the song that they came out in May of 2016 in which they play it in their tour lineup.
This version is different. it is taken from an acoustic youtube video.

song_name: Scandal Of Grace Id Be Lost

performance.name: Live version from "Of Dirt And Grace: Live From The Land"
performance.comment:
"Of Dirt And Grace: Live From The Land" live album was recorded in March 2016 in various places in Israel.
This live version of "Scandal of Grace (I'd Be Lost)" was recorded in front of an empty 1st century tomb not far from Golgotha.

version_description: Capo 4, played in C. Based on the track off the Wonder album.

Acoustic Version tabbed off video at: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ax7tEfenM6k . Key of G to better suit male vocalists. Arrangement in video is a little different (singer has switched the verse placements) but this works for most male vocalists.

Worked out personally on acoustic guitar, simplified chords for acoustic and beginners, easy strum pattern may not be exact but will work. Please leave comments if you have any suggestions and please rate.
